# Tester Integration Flow

When adding a new component to the tester:

1. Register one `ComponentMenuItem` in `ComponentsTesterApp`.
2. Feed the component with sample state from `src/jvmMain/kotlin/com/narvane/sampledata`.
3. Keep `ComponentMenuList` and `ComponentPreviewScreen` generic (do not hardcode component-specific logic there).
4. Ensure the new item title is stable and unique (used as selection key).
5. Keep preview wiring thin: instantiate component and callbacks only.
